WEBVTT

01:48:01.441 --> 01:48:02.733
Sir, you know the route

01:48:03.149 --> 01:48:05.774
Georgekutty took from Kottayam
with Varun's remains, right?

01:48:06.524 --> 01:48:08.108
That twenty-cent plot of land

01:48:08.608 --> 01:48:11.024
on the reserve forest boundary
where Pathro's house is...

01:48:11.691 --> 01:48:13.608
It was Georgekutty
who purchased that land

01:48:14.274 --> 01:48:15.524
five years ago.
